			<a href="http://www.figandcherry.com">Christie @ fig&cherry</a> wrote:<br />
			
			It will take a while - but try steaming them in a bamboo steamer over boiling water. Or even a metal steamer. That way, they won't go mushy (by boiling).<br />
			
			<ol class="commentlist"><li id="comment-1192149">
